
# EcomShopApplication

A simple e-commerce application built with C# and .NET.

## Features

* Product management
* Customer management
* Shopping cart functionality
* Store operations

## Technologies

* C#
* .NET 9
* Visual Studio
* Git & GitHub

## Project Structure

* `Product.cs` - Product model
* `Customer.cs` - Customer model
* `Cart.cs` - Shopping cart functionality
* `Store.cs` - Store management
* `Program.cs` - Application entry point

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Iro-sources/EcomShopApplication.git
```

2. Restore dependencies:

```bash
dotnet restore
```

3. Run the application:

```bash
dotnet run
```

